<info>
Golden Horde was a turkic khanate that existed from 1242 to 1502. Its borders reached from
Crimea to Siberia. It influenced and controlled russian states by a system of tributaries
that were paid by all neighbours of the Horde. Later in 1381 its power declined and it
finally dissolved in 15th century.

Ordian traits are Nomadic and Nomadic, to represent the nomadic character of
the empire and system of tributaries.

Oridan leaders include various khans.
Oridian color is gold and its flag is banner from 1339.
</info>
